reviews.text: I just went last night where the buffet is doing 50% less. The food and the staffs are extremely good.  I would say it is the best buffet that I have in the past few years

Known throughout Hong Kong as having one of the finest hotel buffets, La Scala features a wide range of international cuisines. The spacious restaurant offers both a comfortable uncluttered dining area as well as an open kitchen. Conveniently located in Mongkok, whether a family gathering or an intimate dinner, La Scala will satisfy any appetite.
i visited La scala last July 4 with my Family, foods are good except soup its really salty!
Serving wonderful breakfast with variety of choices in the continental, Japnese, Hong Kong styles
It is inside the mall/hotel.The food is only okay.Popular for families, this there are a lot of kids here.

reviews.text: lunch抵食囉！255成人(已包加一)，有生蠔，有魚生，仲想點? 難得係生蠔唔差，即開，只係過份洗水冇晒海水味。三文魚魚生新鮮，一俾就4片算大方。熟食一般，但算多選擇。甜品可以，以movenpick雪糕最好食。最後，出面自助餐最多咪包一杯飲料，呢道任飲。所以成人255，小孩長者190，堅係性價比高。唔係需要impress特別人的話，呢度自己平平地食，食得過。 完!

食物種類非常多，以酒店自助餐來對比也是算很豐富。
海鮮：長腳蟹，青口，蝦，全都很新鮮，也有熟的龍蝦，
刺身：有六種選擇，可惜沒有希靈魚
生毫：很新鮮，清洗得十分乾淨，現在很多自助餐都沒有生毫了，這裡不貴還供應生毫，十分難得
熟食：由菜，魚，湯，到咖哩都有。當然比較少人會拿拉麵和飯。
切肉：十分推薦他們的切肉，有四種－－羊架、牛肉、豬手、燒春雞，輪流有專人切肉片供應。不得不提伴隨的紫薯很香甜。
芝士：有四款芝士，配搭各種不同的配料，其中香草芝士的芝士味非常香濃，口感一流，過後回甘，是這晚最好吃的食物。
甜品：超級多種類的，接近三分一的區域是擺放甜品的，除了賣相一流，更是非常好吃！拿破輪蛋糕絕對要一試。
總結每人$438是超值之選。

在九龍地方，特別在酒店吃午市自助餐，這裡是一個非常不錯的選擇，連小費， $225港幣，一定能夠吃個飽，而且款式很多

除了一般的熱食，還有泰國船面即叫即制的，海南雞飯充滿風味，還有粥品，西冷牛扒，刺身，竟然有美國的即開即食生蠔，甜蜜的選擇當然也不少，對於這個價錢，絕對沒有投訴，如果喜歡吃自助餐，這裡是一個非常不錯的選擇。

reviews.text: Excellent service and great location!  We got there in the afternoon and they first told us no more 2 beds, then the more experienced gentleman gave us a upgrade .   The staff deserves 5 stars.  The hotel is also very convenient with a shopping mall underneath.  We will be back there next year.

Beautiful hotel with best services.  Every body works here must be trained really well. They are all very polite and professional.  The hotel is in the middle of Mongkok so it is so convenience but it is well maintained. A truly 5 star hotel.
Amazing luxurious hotel! One of the best in Hong Kong! Extremely nice staff. Great facilities including a great pool to swim in and a fairly new gym. The rooms fit all your needs and are very clean.

Clean rooms, nicely furnished. Situated close by the shopping mall so a range of food is always available. Restaurant prices are dear but the staff friendly and helpful. It’s takes a while to get orientated to the hotels position with its several exits.

Hotel is very clean. Staff members are very attentive to our family of six request.  We stayed for 4 days and had to rooms. It felt like home away from home.Food is good and buffet has large variations to select from.  This will be our hotel of choice when we return to Hong Kong. It made our vacation very enjoyable.  Everyone was helpful to assist in our needs or questions about the area and places to see. Check in and out was prompt . Thank you for caring about your guest!
